law.catch_line: Lists not to impede development or use of public or private lands.
law.text: The lists promulgated under KRS 146.610 shall not serve to impede the development or use of public or private lands, including, but not limited to, the normal and accepted operations of agriculture; forestry; mining; development, construction, and maintenance of oil and gas resources and appurtenances; development, construction, and maintenance of utility facilities and appurtenances; construction and maintenance of pipeline rights-of-way; construction activities; equine activities; transportation; or development activities.
law.history: Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1994.
